{"tid":2493592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民眾對國貨欠信心  內地擬7月前准用BNT疫苗","createTime":"2021-04-18T04:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:55:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69f55744a3c3ef4d3f1de689df88baddd2961377","tid":2493592,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210418/73IVZMCCYFHLPDQMGRRAUX7OXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210418%2F73IVZMCCYFHLPDQMGRRAUX7OXA%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=a397ecb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210418%2F73IVZMCCYFHLPDQMGRRAUX7OXA%2F&h=71af1a88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210418/73IVZMCCYFHLPDQMGRRAUX7OXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n民眾對國貨欠信心 <br />\n內地擬7月前准用BNT疫苗<br />\n<br />\n【傳開綠燈】內地近期為推動全民接種疫苗，採取多樣措施，但內地民眾對國產疫苗的信心始終不大。據美媒引述消息指，中國或將在今年7月前批准德國的BioNTech疫苗在國內銷售，相比一眾仍未獲世衞授權的國產疫苗，中方對BioNTech疫苗開綠燈的舉動或成國內民眾的好消息。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：網傳民警打國藥不治「血小板為零」<br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》引述消息人士指，中方官員過去其實一直在審視德國醫藥公司BioNTech和美國輝瑞藥廠聯合研發的BioNTech疫苗臨床試驗數據，並預計將在今年7月前准許在國內銷售該疫苗。事實上，德國BioNTech早在去年12月已同意與上海復星醫藥集團合作，今年為中國提供一億劑疫苗。據該消息人士指，有關時間表是與當局私下討論的初步結論，確切審批時間尚未落實，會取決於中國疫苗在外國的審批情況，相信有關決定一定程度受政治影響。據世衞資料顯示，科興及國藥（北京生物製品研究所）兩款國產疫苗目前正接受世衞的審查，預料最快本月底可得知審查結果，決定是否給予兩者緊急使用授權。而BioNTech疫苗則是最早獲世衞認可的疫苗之一，早在去年底已獲世衞授權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QS7ZctWodKtRDZeQnccVj5sDxpE=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RS2J33RVNJBZ5M2ZZZSJSUSXIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQS7ZctWodKtRDZeQnccVj5sDxpE%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRS2J33RVNJBZ5M2ZZZSJSUSXIE.jpg&h=a3c734fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■北京故宮有流動疫苗接種車，「古裝人」躍躍欲試。<br />\n<br />\n德國BioNTech指，正努力準備在當局批准後向中國供貨，但上海復星、國家衞健委和藥品監督管理局暫未回應事件。商界一直均希望中方承認海外研發的疫苗，以便利商務旅行。上海美國商會指，BioNTech疫苗在全球獲較多國家承認，自去年12月已經提出希望中方認可BioNTech疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n內地現在正積極推動全民接種疫苗。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"483499e5a4262c85e53f127e075fc43f246678e2","tid":2493592,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔好呀 唔好同文明世界爭"},{"pid":"6421d3da64baadffe9de387b395da8342760463b","tid":2493592,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"483499e5a4262c85e53f127e075fc43f246678e2","tid":2493592,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔好呀 唔好同文明世界爭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"香港都係跟上海復星買<br />\n今次冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ee4ea8a248f9c2e0edd2de8166120c104d243a","tid":2493592,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"呢啲post就無五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5c24ec63b4ef2f01842ceba8d9c298a284fc9e","tid":2493592,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"口裏說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d5445c218589bae5fc669a49a238444e272a49","tid":2493592,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得話冇得打啦<br />\n俾撚晒大陸<br />\n（做２等公民就係咁）"},{"pid":"aa4d99e3cbe87ae1587820001bf799e09a182b90","tid":2493592,"uid":60109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"已經喺香港做完醫療實驗"},{"pid":"9eb21e80dd3104399d2b270420696b823c114ba3","tid":2493592,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"483499e5a4262c85e53f127e075fc43f246678e2","tid":2493592,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"唔好呀 唔好同文明世界爭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"唔緊要喇<br />\n<br />\n成班香港戇鳩有得打都唔打<br />\n<br />\n一陣俾d狗拖出去打科興做test就好笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住大陸打哂復必泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22b9ded0c131e3cea23f93baab718bcebc1db36","tid":2493592,"uid":287269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"根本大陸可以迫人打，仲引入係因為國產唔 work"},{"pid":"80326bdf6aa4a984c787edf46c622bff04f3714e","tid":2493592,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"香港藍絲蠢過支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}